dct_title_s: A new map of Egypt, from the latest authorities / by John Cary, engraver. [copy 2]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by hachures. Appears in Cary's new universal atlas. 1808. Inset: The Delta and adjacent parts, upon an enlarged scale. Label affixed to verso: 49.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published by J. Cary, engraver & mapseller, no. 181 Strand, June 1st 1805.
